data.desc: Develop multiple NOBI services for our users and our internal team

- Develop Titik Pintar API that is being used in our mobile application, internal application, and other application.
- Develop Titik Pintar Admin Panel for our internal team.
- Develop Sahabat Pintar (https://sahabatpintar.id), both backend and frontend, for public use. That is a website for teachers, designers, and animators to contribute to our learning application
- Develop Titik Pintar Account Login. That is a website for parents to monitor their children's progress in our application
- Develop some features like multiplayer, live class, automation, and others for both our users and our internal team

This is my first job after I graduate. This is a software house company. I do a lot of Laravel work here. Some apps that I build or develop are BMM, BLK, an app for a church, Datapandi, my company website, an app for one of a hospital in Jakarta, and many more. Some of this app already finished and others still developing.

This was my internship at my college. In my internship, I do Quality Assurance, developed an app, and make an app. An app that I QA is an app called Virtual Cubicle. This app is for a company called PT PLN Enjiniring (PT. Prima Layanan Nasional Enjiniring). I also develop an app called BPP. This app is for my internal company. An last an app that I make is an app called SILISA. This is a prototype app for Kementerian Energi dan Sumber Daya Mineral Republik Indonesia.
